text: Jonas Augustin Westman (28 August 1909 - 20 June 1983) was a Swedish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. Westman attended university in England at Balliol College, Oxford. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Swedish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Sweden Category:People from Luleå Category:Westman family Category:Alumni of Balliol College, Oxford Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics
